reviews.review_text: Hometown Show Great recording of the first show of 1984, a very good year.

1984 kick off This show is a little rough around the edges and features what sounds like a pretty fucked up Bobby with technical issues. Still, I love the quality of the recording, and Brent and Jerry do some insane things throughout. Strong first set, cool China/Rider. Some special performances due to Bobby issues (Babe it Aint No Lie).
